Program: Thinking Allowed
Title: Post-Truth
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b0bk1llv
Last Broadcast Date: Mon 24 Sep 2018
Post-Truth – Laurie Taylor explores a very modern phenomenon, or is it? He’s joined by Steve Fuller, Professor of Sociology at the University of Warwick, Helen Pluckrose, Editor of Areo, a digital magazine focused on Enlightenment liberalism and Andrew Chadwick, Professor of Political Communication at Loughborough University. Producer: Jayne Egerton Show less